manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Dual Coated Surface Oleophobic and hydrophobic coating to resist oils, sweat, etc. Ultra-Transparent Ultra-transparent HD visuals to match the beauty of the iPhone. Anti-scratch Protector Anti-scratch protector helps prevent scratches from minor drops.

Introducing Trianium's 3 Pack Glass Screen Protector Compatible with iPhone 13 and iPhone 13 Pro 2021 A 3-Pack of screen protectors from Trianium specially designed for the iPhone 13/13 Pro (6.1-inch Screen Display). A powerful anti-scratch surface and dual special coating to help prevent fingerprints, oils, sweat, and liquids from the surface of the screen. Plus, full frontal Face ID compatibility with all the recent iPhone features and functionalities. Go Trianium. Go Bold. Anti-Scratch Surface: Help prevent scratches from minor-drops or tight pockets. Face ID Compatibility: Full frontal face ID compatibility alongside all other iPhone features. Fingerprint-Free: A dual special coating helps to prevent fingerprints, oils, sweat, and more. Installation Note Clean the phone screen thoroughly using the wet & dry wipes before installation. Then, clean the phone with the Dust Absorber sticker to eliminate any debris on the screen. Put the alignment frame on the iPhone. Peel off the protective layer (with tab) from the screen protector before applying to the phone. If air bubbles are present, use squeegee or hard card to push bubble from the center away to the edge of the phone screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressive protection and an absolute no-brainer for the price
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been using this brand for years but gained a new appreciation for it today. I dropped my phone into my La-Z-Boy and didn’t realize it until I heard a horrible grinding sound upon swiveling. I’m not sure exactly what happened, but the metal internal mechanism of the recliner cleaner tested my Trianium screen protector. The protector took 99% of the punishment; there is just a minor cosmetic scratch on the screen itself. Given this could have been pretty catastrophic (the Apple leather case I had on is a complete goner), I am impressed and grateful. Just ordered another 3-pack to have on hand after installing the last one that came in this kit!Prior to this, I’ve only damaged a Trianium protector once through many minor drops. Zero damage to the phone itself.The screen protector is easy to install, and I’ve never run into major bubbles.Highly recommend this brand!
